caller_intent: The caller requested a car insurance quote but was informed that the agent could not provide auto insurance alone due to policy requirements.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the call was from Lions Insurance and asked how they could assist.
Caller requested a car insurance quote.
Agent explained that current carriers require either a homeowners or renters policy in addition to auto insurance.
Caller declined the offer and ended the conversation.
summary: A caller requested a car insurance quote but was informed that the agent could not provide auto insurance alone due to carrier requirements for additional coverage (homeowners/renters). The caller declined and ended the conversation.
